{"title":"共和国当铭记（三首）","authors":["高凯"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":9,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"共和国当铭记（三首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高凯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘胡兰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你把五个绣花的手指"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攥成拳头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党的旗帜为你红透"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那天起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你更英姿飒爽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那天起，你便知道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一个目标十分美好"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从那天起，你便看到"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮丽还在身后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人一口气咔嚓了六个同志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叫十五岁的你看什么叫死"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你早知道那是怎么一回事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没眨眼就走过去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让誓词变成画面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当你的头枕在铡刀另一边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你告诉刽子手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕死的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是共产党员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"董存瑞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是一个非常时刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总攻已经开始"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人的六挺机枪"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伸出血淋淋的火舌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吞舔你和你的战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那一刻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你突然挺成一根铁柱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将那包沉重的仇恨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举上头顶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轰隆一声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你用肩试了试天空的重量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便光芒万丈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从此"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你把去隆化中学的道路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"打扫得干干净净"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新中国在隆化中学"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一批一批育人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄继光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人用照明弹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把第五个夜晚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得如同白天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们走在弹雨里……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仅仅一瞬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当那铁家伙哑然无声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当上甘岭哑然无声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而你的胸膛里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却是阵阵枪声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好大好大的胸膛呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明时分"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是硝烟滚滚……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在扑向枪眼时"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是站起又倒下的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但归根结底"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是倒下又站起的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：甘肃省西峰市陇东日报社）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}